            <p>Cherry-picking 2013 as a starting year for bitcoin's outperformance is the standard skeptic's objection. So pick any other year. From every starting year since 2014 &mdash; through every bear market, every drawdown, every 'cycle is over' moment &mdash; <em>$1 invested in bitcoin outperformed $1 invested in housing by orders of magnitude.</em> The toggle lets you choose your own starting point and see for yourself.</p>
        </div>

